{"created": "2026-03-20T16:35:13.820274+00:00", "modified": "2026-03-20T16:35:14.227721+00:00", "id": 19135345, "conceptrecid": "17715051", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.19135345", "conceptdoi": "10.5281/zenodo.17715051", "doi_url": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19135345", "metadata": {"title": "Dataset associated with \"The effects of VRNT on clinical and neuroimaging outcomes in patients with chronic back pain: a randomized clinical trial\"", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.19135345", "publication_date": "2026-03-11", "description": "<p>Dataset associated with Ceko et al. 2024 PAIN DOI: 10.1097/j.pain.0000000000003198</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Clinical outcomes</strong></p>\n<p>Stored in HEAL_data.xlsx</p>\n<p>See Tab 1 for variables and coding scheme.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>See Tabs 2 - 7 for scored variables:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>participant-level</li>\n<li>pain intensity, interference, bothersomeness</li>\n<li>Pain Catastrophizing (PCS)</li>\n<li>Kinesiophobia (TSK)&nbsp;</li>\n<li>OLBP, SF-12</li>\n<li>PROMIS</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Neuroimaging outcomes</strong></p>\n<p>CONN02_age_sex &ndash; functional connectivity results</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Group results, controlled for age and sex, per ROI</li>\n<li>Subject-level data per ROI</li>\n</ul>\n<p>TBSS &ndash; white matter results</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Group_age_sex\n<ul>\n<li>Subject-level FA data: all_FA_skeletonized.nii.gz</li>\n<li>Subject-level pre vs. post (difference scores) FA data: merged_postpre.nii.gz</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Pain_age_sex\n<ul>\n<li>Regression with pain scores (VRNT condition), controlled for age and sex</li>\n<li>Subject-level data: all_FA_skeletonized.nii.gz</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Notes on data preprocessing and analysis&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>Behavioral data were analyzed using custom code in MATLAB 2020b.</p>\n<p>Resting-state functional MRI data were preprocessed using fmriprep 21.0.0 and analyzed using CONN 20.b, running on SPM12 in MATLAB 2018b.</p>\n<p>Diffusion-weighted MRI data were preprocessed using QSIprep. FA maps were derived using DTIFIT in TBSS and statistical analysis was carried out using TBSS in FSL.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>", "access_right": "open", "creators": [{"name": "CEKO, MARTA", "affiliation": "University of Colorado Boulder", "orcid": "0000-0001-8679-8145"}, {"name": "WAGER, TOR", "affiliation": "University of Colorado Boulder", "orcid": "0000-0002-1936-5574"}, {"name": "Baeuerle, Tassilo", "affiliation": null, "orcid": "0000-0001-5213-7605"}, {"name": "Lumley, Mark", "affiliation": null, "orcid": "0000-0001-7095-8378"}], "contributors": [{"name": "WAGER, TOR", "affiliation": "University of Colorado Boulder", "type": "Researcher", "orcid": "0000-0002-1936-5574"}, {"name": "Baeuerle, Tassilo", "affiliation": null, "type": "Researcher", "orcid": "0000-0001-5213-7605"}, {"name": "Lumley, Mark", "affiliation": null, "type": "Researcher", "orcid": "0000-0001-7095-8378"}, {"name": "Webster, Lynn", "affiliation": null, "type": "Researcher"}], "keywords": ["Pre-Post", "fMRI", "DTI"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "10.1097/j.pain.0000000000003198", "relation": "isDescribedBy", "resource_type": "publication-article", "scheme": "doi"}], "dates": [{"type": "available", "description": "behavioral outcomes"}], "version": "v2", "references": ["DOI: 10.1097/j.pain.0000000000003198"], "language": "eng", "resource_type": {"title": "Dataset", "type": "dataset"}, "journal": {"issue": "8", "pages": "1860-1874", "title": "PAIN", "volume": "165"}, "license": {"id": "cc-by-4.0"}, "grants": [{"code": "R43NR017575", "internal_id": "01y3zfr79::R43NR017575", "funder": {"name": "National Institute of Nursing Research"}}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 1, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "17715051"}}]}}, "title": "Dataset associated with \"The effects of VRNT on clinical and neuroimaging outcomes in patients with chronic back pain: a randomized clinical trial\"", "links": {"self": "htt